disper (0.3.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New point release
  * Works with newer nVidia drivers that support XRandR 1.2
  * Finish XDG configuration in ~/.disper/config (old location still supported)
  * A number of small bug fixes.

 -- Willem van Engen <dev-disper@willem.engen.nl>  Tue, 23 Apr 2013 11:59:23 +0200

disper (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * New major release
  * Hook functionality in ~/.disper/hooks and /usr/share/disper/hooks
  * Default configuration in ~/.disper/config
  * Allow "max" resolution for clone
  * A number of small bug fixes.

 -- Willem van Engen <dev-disper@willem.engen.nl>  Thu, 05 May 2011 13:27:36 +0200

disper (0.2.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * New point release
  * Make disper work with non-release Python versions (closes lp:#360100)
  * Add option to switch to secondary screen (patch contributed by Arjan Scherpenisse)

 -- Willem van Engen <dev-disper@willem.engen.nl>  Thu, 21 May 2009 12:25:09 +0200

disper (0.2.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * New point release
  * Work on older XRandR systems and workaround ctypes trouble
    (closes lp:#338978)
  * Work on Python versions 2.3 and 2.4 as well
  * Remove trailing zero from string query replies (closes lp:#337721)

 -- Willem van Engen <dev-disper@willem.engen.nl>  Thu, 09 Apr 2009 21:38:32 +0200

disper (0.2.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New point release
  * Detect DFP scaling from ~/.nvidia-settings-rc or override on command-line
    (closes lp:#315139)
  * Don't crash when DISPLAY is invalid (closes lp:#327133)
  * Make panel placement consistent on switch by setting Xinerama details
    (closes lp:#321288)
  * Make switching between single displays work when they are disconnected at
    the time of switch (not all cases are covered yet, laptops should be ok)
    (closes lp:#315920)

 -- Willem van Engen <dev-disper@willem.engen.nl>  Fri, 13 Feb 2009 16:47:52 +0100

